text: Kamau Sadiki Leverock was born 19 October, 1994. He is a Bermudian cricketer who played 29 Twenty20 Internationals for Bermuda. He is the nephew of former cricketers Dwayne Leverock and Alvin Greenidge. ==Other websites== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Bermudian cricketers
